description.@value: イブン・バットゥータの大旅行の記録。タンジャ出発からエジプトまでの記述ではアレクサンドリア・カイロについての記述を含む。シリアへの旅ではガザ・エルサレム・アレッポ・ダマスクスについて記し、メディナ・メッカへの旅やカーバ神殿について記す。

From Ibn Battuta’s departure in Tangiers to his arrival in Egypt, the narrative includes descriptions of Alexandria and Cairo. It also includes his journey to Syria, where he visited Gaza and Jerusalem, Aleppo, and Damascus; as well as his pilgrimage to Mecca, including his visit to the Kaaba.
